=========================================================
万物一心（Unison）Multi-Agent Collaboration Bridge

Loads ``pipeline.yaml``, validates required fields and runtimes,
constructs an immutable ``PipelineSpec``, and provides a ``dry_run``
check for prompt-file existence.
